        "created_at": "2025-07-16T03:37:22.340Z",
        "cooked": "<p>First\uff0c Thank you.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Have you tried with 2-3 GRV proxies and 1-2 commit proxies?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Currently have not tried\u3002 In my production environment, the expected data volume is 500 TB, with an anticipated KV read QPS of 300 K and KV write QPS of 100K. Now I\u2019m planning to run a stress test, do you have any recommendations for the number and ratio of GRV proxies and commit proxies?</p>",
