        "created_at": "2025-07-17T08:14:24.293Z",
        "cooked": "<p>1 stateless process we put on ssd disk (256Gb)<br>\n2 on start we have 3 TLog per disk, and 4 SS per disk (3TL + 4SS per host)<br>\n4 we are try decrease it<br>\n6 we are checking <code>status json</code> and system metrics, status show about 100% for tlog and ss, but total metrics per disk is much lower then we got by fio test. In this test we received 50k IOPS + 700MB/s, current saturation is 15k IOPS + 5MB/S (TLog)<br>\n7 now, we can\u2019t do it, we can request only typical hardware configuration from infra department</p>\n<p>PS total workload now:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>read ops 37K/s</li>\n<li>write ops 10K/s</li>\n<li>transactions 10K/s</li>\n<li>conflicts 20 ops/s</li>\n<li>keys read 82K/s</li>\n<li>bytes read 210 MB/s</li>\n<li>bytes write 22 MB/s</li>\n</ul>",
