        "created_at": "2025-07-17T09:40:11.635Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>9 hosts total - 3 host per datahall</li>\n<li>3 individual disk: 1 SSD (system) + 2 NVME 3Tb (TLog/SS)</li>\n<li>120 Core (2 CPU)</li>\n<li>512 Gb RAM</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>You should have <em>only one TLog per disk</em>. For SS, you should have 3 max. for most NVMes<br>\nThis should improve performance</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>We have already planned to reduce the number of TLogs and check your suggest.</p>\n<p>Our target is 20K-30K TPS on write and 20+K read TPS (snapshot with GRV Cache).</p>",
